org.efs.openreports.util

Class SearchResultsTableDecorator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.displaytag.decorator.TableDecorator
      • org.efs.openreports.util.SearchResultsTableDecorator

  • public class SearchResultsTableDecorator
extends org.displaytag.decorator.TableDecorator
    The SearchResultsTableDecorator class is a DisplayTag TableDecorator used to populate the Action and Tags columns of a DisplayTag table. These columns are generated based on the class of the current row object. Currently only Report, ReportGroup, and ReportUser classes are supported.
